FBIS4-9147 "dreeu077_i_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-077 Daily Report 21 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Situation in Gorazde -- 21 April Situation in Gorazde -- 21 April Serbs Closing on Town LD2104090094 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 0800 GMT 21 Apr 94 LD2104090094 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] The tragedy of Gorazde goes on. Thousands of shells have been destroying the center of the town while from the surrounding hills the chetniks are using their snipers and anti-aircraft weapons to monitor every movement in the town. No one can tell how many casualties there has been in the town. From all directions tanks are closing on the town center. According to as yet unconfirmed reports reaching the UN Protection Force [UNPROFOR] headquarters in Zagreb, Serb tanks are moving in the direction of part of the town which contains a munitions factory currently in Muslim hands.
